        <div class="eyebrow">About Dr. Sri</div>
        <h2>A decade of dedicated dental care across Delhi NCR</h2>

        <p>
          Dr. Sri is a Delhi NCR-based dental surgeon with over 10 years of
          clinical experience in endodontics, cosmetic dentistry, and full-mouth
          implant rehabilitation. Trained at a leading Indian dental college and
          certified in advanced implantology, Dr. Sri has treated over 5,000
          patients from Delhi, Noida, Gurgaon, and Ghaziabad with a gentle,
          patient-first approach.
        </p>

